-- Aquarius Platinum to Appeal Implementation of Order to Limit Mining Areas
-- Victoria Batchelor
-- 2010-07-18T22:36:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-18/aquarius-platinum-to-appeal-implementation-of-order-to-limit-mining-areas.html

          
          
             Aquarius Platinum Ltd. said it will
be formally appealing against the implementation of the
directive by the Principal Inspector of the North West Region,
at 3 p.m. South African time today. At this appeal, Aquarius
will present alternative strategies to ensure safer and at the
same time, sustainable bord and pillar operations.  
          
          


  


        